<fr:li><fr:strong>Inductive argument:</fr:strong> For arbitrary <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>, prove the claim "If <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[P[n]]]></fr:tex> then <fr:tex
