<fr:p><fr:strong>Base Case:</fr:strong> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n=1]]></fr:tex>. Then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\Bbbk =\mathbb {F}]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex
