display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {F}]]></fr:tex> be a field, let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f(x)\in \mathbb {F}[x]]]></fr:tex> be a polynomial. If <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n=\deg (f)]]></fr:tex>, then there exists a field extension <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\Bbbk  / \mathbb {F}]]></fr:tex> of degree at most <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n!]]></fr:tex>such that <fr:tex
